OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FAnother very mild, though fairly
OL,7,Fcloudy day on Wednesday with patchy
OL,8,Frain in the west. Cooling down
OL,9,Fthereafter and turning more unsettled,
OL,10,Fwith rain and strong winds possible at
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
